thread.title: EastEnders

author: Fiona Flynn
title: EastEnders
text: Kathy is feeling the guilt big time tonight, so much so that she tells Ben she isn't sure if she can really go through with their plan, but he urges her not to back out now as they need to save Phil. However, Jane is soon starting to question Kathy's motives while Ian then later drops a bombshell on his mum. Presumably to tell her about that 'child of Satan' grandson of hers... surely Ian couldn't have any more bombshells than that up his sleeve?
